#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiriki; is an addictive and fun dice game by &kde;, designed to be played "
"by as many as six players. Participants have to collect points by rolling "
"five dice for up to three times per single turn. Each roll generates a "
"specific combination of numbers which the player is free to either accept or "
"decline. However, each specific combination of numbers can be accepted only "
"once. After thirteen turns the game ends and the scores are compared. The "
"player with the largest amount of points wins the game."
msgstr ""
"&kiriki; on &kde; kûÑitev ja lûçbus tûÊringumûÊng, mida vûçib mûÊngida kuni kuus "
"mûÊngijat. MûÊngijad peavad koguma punkte, veeretades selleks û¥hes voorus viit "
"tûÊringut kuni kolm korda. Iga viskega tekib teatav arvukombinatsioon, "
"millega mûÊngija vûçib rahule jûÊûÊda vûçi mitte. Iga kombinatsiooni saab aga "
"ainult û¥he korra kasutada. PûÊrast kolmeteistkû¥mnendat vooru mûÊng lûçpeb ja "
"vûçrreldakse saadud tulemusi. MûÊngu vûçidab suurima punktisumma kogunud "
"mûÊngija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kuidas mûÊngida"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "EesmûÊrk:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Earn more score points than either of the opponents."
msgstr "koguda rohkem punkte kui teised mûÊngijad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once &kiriki; starts, it right away gives out the first combination for the "
"player one. If you are the player one, then it is now your turn, otherwise "
"you will have to wait until all other players make their moves."
msgstr ""
"&kiriki; kûÊivitamisel antakse mûÊngijale kohe kombinatsioon ette. Kui oled "
"esimene mûÊngija, saad sellega otsemaid nûçustuda vûçi uuesti veeretada, kui "
"mitte, pead ootama oma viskejûÊrjekorda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:78 index.docbook:80 index.docbook:84 index.docbook:86
#: index.docbook:241 index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "MûÊrkus:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, unless the game settings have been changed, and in single player "
"mode, the first player is controlled by human (you), while all other five "
"players are controlled by Artificial Intelligence."
msgstr ""
"Kui mûÊnguseadistusi ei ole muudetud ning mûÊngitakse û¥ksikmûÊngija reéƒiimis, "
"juhib esimest mûÊngijat inimene (sina), teisi aga arvuti tehisaju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once it is your turn, the first thing you should do is examine the current "
"roll. Each of the five dice on the left hand side of the game screen has a "
"specific value. Check the sequence to see if these values form any of the "
"score patterns."
msgstr ""
"Kui jûçuab kûÊtte sinu kord, tuleks kûçigepealt hoolikalt uurida tûÊringuid. "
"Igal mûÊngulaua vasakus servas asuval viiel tûÊringul on oma vûÊûÊrtus. Uuri "
"neid hoolikalt, et nûÊha, kas neist saab kokku panna mûçne vajaliku "
"kombinatsiooni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80 index.docbook:86
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The detailed description of the score pattern values can be found in the "
#| "<link linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">ãGame Rules, Strategies and Tipsã</link> "
#| "section of this handbook."
msgid ""
"The detailed description of the score pattern values can be found in the "
"<link linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Game Rules, Strategies and Tips</link> "
"section of this handbook."
msgstr ""
"Kombinatsioonide vûÊûÊrtusi kirjeldab tûÊpsemalt osa <link linkend="
"\"rules_and_tips\">MûÊngureeglid, strateegia ja nûçuanded</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that the combination can match more than one score pattern. In "
"this case you will have to determine which score pattern will result in "
"greater points for you."
msgstr ""
"Pane tûÊhele, et mûçnikord vûçivad tûÊringud pakkuda vûçimalust mitmeks "
"kombinatsiooniks. Sel juhul tuleb otsustada, milline neist annab rohkem "
"punkte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case the current sequence matches no score pattern, or matches a score "
"pattern you have already used up, you have two more rolls to fix the "
"situation. To use your second (third) roll select the dice you are not "
"satisfied with by clicking on them with your mouse and click the "
"<guibutton>Roll</guibutton> button located right under the dice. This will "
"cause the dice in question to reroll, thus changing their values."
msgstr ""
"Kui tûÊringute vûÊûÊrtused ei moodusta mingit kindlat kombinatsiooni vûçi "
"sobivad konbinatsioonile, mille oled juba ûÊra kasutanud, saad tûÊringuid veel "
"kaks korda veeretada, et olukorda parandada. Teise vûçi kolmanda viske puhul "
"klûçpsa tûÊringutel, mille vûÊûÊrtusega sa ei ole rahul, ning klûçpsa tûÊringute "
"all asuvale nupule <guibutton>Veereta</guibutton>. Sel juhul veeretatakse "
"valitud tûÊringuid ning neile ilmuvad uued vûÊûÊrtused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have done the third reroll you must choose the score pattern which "
"fits the dice sequence on hand. If none of the score patterns fit the "
"sequence - you can either use <guilabel>Chance</guilabel> score pattern, or "
"just select any score pattern on your scoreboard."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled sooritanud kolmanda viske, pead valima kombinatsiooni, millele "
"tûÊringute vûÊûÊrtused omistada. Kui û¥kski kombinatsioon ei sobi sinu tûÊringute "
"vûÊûÊrtustega, vûçid kasutada ka kombinatsiooni <guilabel>Vaba valik</guilabel> "
"vûçi siis valida mis tahes kombinatsiooni, mis annaks vûÊhemalt mingeidki "
"punkte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a score pattern that does not fit current dice sequence, the "
"score pattern you select will become void and of zero value."
msgstr ""
"Kui valid kombinatsiooni, mis û¥ldse tûÊringute vûÊûÊrtustega ei sobi, saad "
"selle kombinatsiooni eest null punkti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As soon as you choose the score pattern its value updates to reflect the "
"dice sequence you currently have."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled kombinatsiooni valinud, ilmub selle juures kohe nûÊhtavale teenitud "
"punktisumma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right after that your turn ends and the next participantãs turn begins. This "
"sequence repeats some thirteen times and then the game ends, the scores are "
"calculated and the high scores are awarded."
msgstr ""
"SeejûÊrel asuvad teised mûÊngijad tûÊringuid veeretama. Nii kordub kolmteist "
"korda ning siis mûÊng lûçpeb, tulemused arvutatakse kokku ja pannakse paika "
"mûÊngijate paremusjûÊrjestus."

