"Esimese veeretamise jûÊrel vûçib mûÊngija sooritada veel kuni kaks viset (kokku "
"kolm viset vooru kohta)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Player is not obligated to perform additional rolls if the first roll "
"brings satisfactory results."
msgstr ""
"MûÊngija ei pea lisaviskeid sooritama, kui juba esimese veeretamise tulemus "
"on igati rahuldav."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each additional roll may either involve all the dice, or only the selected "
"ones."
