"Iga lisaviske puhul vûçib veeretada kas kûçiki vûçi ainult valitud tûÊringuid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A Player can select the dice to be recast by clicking on them with the mouse."
