"Kui tûÊringut on uuesti veeretatud, lûÊheb selle eelnev vûÊûÊrtus kaotsi ja "
"kehtima jûÊûÊb ainult veeretamisel vûÊlja tulnud vûÊûÊrtus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result of the roll is considered satisfactory if the values of the dice "
"on display can be put into one of the score patterns discussed above."
